data.description: The secret is out! Riverview is the place to be. Gorgeous Riverview home, original owner/contractor built, has demonstrated detailed and innovated construction. This beautiful 3441 sq ft, 4 bd, 2.5 bath home backs to a local favorite walking trail that leads to the Carson River and miles of trials. Mature secluded landscaped backyard, with area for a garden. Inside the home enjoy a fabulous sunroom weatherized for summer or winter time. Real wood floors through the upstairs for a warm, comfortable look. Wonderful entertaining size kitchen with a fabulous panty, gas cooktop on island, and bright, sunny breakfast nook, large spacious pantry. Each bedroom is generously sized with nice sized closets. The master bedroom boasts a gorgeous, slider out to the balcony view, large master bath, garden tub, and an extra-large walk-in closet. Downstairs hosts two large bedrooms, extra storage rooms, water heater has a backup tankless water heater all set for future replacement, downstairs family bonus room is bright and sunny with a gorgeous patio that leads to the beautiful fully landscaped back yard. Separate dog run and garden to utilize and enjoy.  This home includes so many extras. Central vac, owned water softener, large extra high ceilings in the 3-car insulated and finished, garage. Side yard is wide enough to accommodate RV's and toys. Fully fenced and gated. New interior and exterior paint, this home shows pride of ownership throughout. Enjoy living in the desirable Riverview neighborhood, close to town but feels like you're in the country. Carson River is a short walk way. Discover all the new walking and bike trails in the area. This is your forever home to enjoy!
